# AstraX Bot – Privacy Policy

Last Updated: March 4, 2026


## 1. Overview

This Privacy Policy explains what data AstraX processes and how it is used.

AstraX operates exclusively within Discord and processes data only as necessary to provide its functionality.


## 2. Message Content Processing

AstraX may process message content in servers where it is installed strictly for:

* Executing commands
* Applying moderation rules
* Keyword-based automated moderation
* Logging deleted or edited messages

Message content is only processed within servers where the Bot is present.

Processing of message content complies with Discord’s Message Content Intent Policy.


## 3. Data Processed

The Bot may process:

* Discord user IDs
* Server IDs
* Channel IDs
* Role IDs
* Message IDs
* Invite usage data
* Moderation records
* Giveaway participation data
* Configuration settings

This data is used solely to operate the Bot’s features.


## 4. Temporary Data and Cache

The Bot may temporarily store data in memory to:

* Track invite usage
* Manage active moderation actions
* Process commands
* Maintain session-based functionality

Temporary data may be cleared automatically during restarts or updates.


## 5. Data We Do Not Collect

We do not collect:

* Passwords
* Email addresses
* Authentication tokens
* Payment information
* Location data
* Third-party analytics data

We do not sell or share personal data with third parties.


## 6. Data Usage

Collected data is used only to:

* Enforce moderation actions
* Operate logging systems
* Manage giveaways
* Provide invite statistics
* Process bug reports
* Maintain system stability

Data is never used for advertising or profiling.


## 7. Data Retention

Data is retained only as long as necessary to provide the Bot’s functionality.

* Temporary moderation data is removed when it expires.
* Configuration data remains until modified or deleted.
* If the Bot is removed from a server, associated data may be deleted within a reasonable timeframe.


## 8. Data Access

Access to operational data is restricted to the Bot operators.

We do not sell, trade, or distribute user data.


## 9. Security

Reasonable technical measures are implemented to protect processed data.
However, no system can guarantee absolute security.


## 10. User Rights

You may:

* Request deletion of your associated data
* Ask a server administrator to remove the Bot
* Contact us regarding privacy concerns


## 11. Contact

For privacy-related inquiries:

* Submit a support ticket in the AstraX Support Server or in our support section on our website.
* Website: https://astrax.my
* Discord: https://discord.gg/AstraX
